Investors should switch to Asian
technology stocks from China consumer companies, according to
Credit Suisse Group AG’s Sakthi Siva and Kin Nang Chik.  “Tech is priced for disappointment while China consumer is
priced for perfection,” according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
